This paper is primarily focused on the training of neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the impact of the learning rate on the performance of the network, which is a common topic in the subfield of neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper uses the CIFAR-10 dataset, which is commonly used in computer vision research (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the generalization of the network, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
